name: AI Data Science Templates Addons for Elementor
author: codenpy

sections.description:
AI Data Science Templates Kit for Elementor

plugin will allow you to build awesome stunning Ai and Data science home pages and inner pages with only single click. Super and fast way to show modern templates inside elementor page builder with 3 home pages and 3 inner pages. AI and data science addons best for any ai and data science template. You will have 3 complete ai and data science template with one click template import.

There are more than 38+ addons with 5 ready to use templates, just you need to edit it with your own content.

Live Demo

Widgets List

  • Hero Section
  • About Us
  • Heading
  • Compare
  • Api Box
  • Faq
  • Team Member
  • Partners
  • Single Service
  • Service Section

Tags: elementor page builder, elementor template, kit, elementor, addon, widget, template, ai, data science, analysis, page template, responsive, responsive image effects, css3 effects, image style, service box, feature box, icon, animation, plugin, wordpress.

Features

  • 3 Stunning Home Pages
  • 3 inner pages
  • One Click Demo Import
  • Customization
  • Super easy Installation.
  • SEO friendly.
  • Easy user interface.
  • Works with any theme.
  • All Major browser supported.
sections.installation:
1. Upload the plugin files to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory, or upload the .zip file with the plugin under Plugins > Add New > Upload.
  2. Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ screen in WordPress
  3. Navigate to Elementor -> AI Data Science Templates for Elementor to import templates
